<p>XI<br/>we had no shelter and temperature as you know was for days 10&deg; below freezing.  I wonder we didn't lose half of them altogether &ndash; (I find on reading the foregoing that the word "horses" appears nearly every second line, but I wrote hurriedly so please forgive the careless phrasing)<br/>regarding my allotment - I am making an extra allotment today payable from 30th September 1917 to you</p>
